<patch call_xgo_precheck>
# Description: Add xgoPrecheck call at the top of cmd/go's main().
# This allows xgo to intercept Go command invocations before standard logic runs.
# Inserted before: if args[0] ==
# After: if xgoPrecheck(args[0], args[1:]) { return; };\nif args[0] ==
goto func main
match if args[0] ==
insert_before if xgoPrecheck(args[0], args[1:]) { return; };
</patch>
